snippet.title: Planet of Lana - Day of the Devs Gameplay reveal 2022
snippet.description:
Adam Stjärnljus, Creative Director at Wishfully, guides you through the gameplay of Planet of Lana. Sign up at our newsletter on planetoflana.com or wishlist on Steam: bit.ly/PlanetOfLana

Planet of Lana is a puzzle adventure game framed by an epic sci-fi saga that stretches across centuries and galaxies.
